html":"{}</p>"},"ps2.7:26.1":{"pli":"<b>Dhammacakkan</b>ti kenaṭṭhena dhammacakkaṁ? ","html":"<p>{}"},"ps2.7:26.2":{"pli":"Dhammañca pavatteti cakkañcāti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.3":{"pli":"Cakkañca pavatteti dhammañcāti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.4":{"pli":"Dhammena pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.5":{"pli":"Dhammacariyāya pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.6":{"pli":"Dhamme ṭhito pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.7":{"pli":"Dhamme patiṭṭhito pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.8":{"pli":"Dhamme patiṭṭhāpento pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.9":{"pli":"Dhamme vasippatto pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.10":{"pli":"Dhamme vasiṁ pāpento pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.11":{"pli":"Dhamme pāramippatto pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.12":{"pli":"Dhamme pāramiṁ pāpento pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ …pe… ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.13":{"pli":"dhammaṁ apacāyamāno pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.14":{"pli":"Dhammaddhajo pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.15":{"pli":"Dhammaketu pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.16":{"pli":"Dhammādhipateyyo pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:26.17":{"pli":"Taṁ kho pana dhammacakkaṁ appaṭivattiyaṁ samaṇena vā brāhmaṇena vā devena vā mārena vā brahmunā vā kenaci vā lokasminti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}</p>"},"ps2.7:27.1":{"pli":"“Saddhindriyaṁ dhammo. ","html":"<p>{}"},"ps2.7:27.2":{"pli":"Taṁ dhammaṁ pavattetī”ti—dhammacakkaṁ …pe… ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:27.3":{"pli":"amatogadhaṁ nibbānaṁ pariyosānaṭṭhena dhammo. ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:27.4":{"pli":"Taṁ dhammaṁ pavattetīti—dhammacakkaṁ. ","html":"{}</p>"},"ps2.7:28.1":{"pli":"Ayaṁ vīriyasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgato iddhipādoti pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṁ udapādi …pe… ","html":"<p>{}"},"ps2.7:28.2":{"pli":"āloko udapādi …pe… ","html":"{}"},"ps2.7:28.3":{"pli":"so 